16. c3 Nxd4 17. Qxd4 Be7 $1 {The most simple path to finish Black's development
} 18. Bxe7 (18. Qxd5+ Be6 19. Qf3+ Kg8 20. Bxe7 Qxe7 21. Rxb7 $2 Qg5 $40 {
