Rxb7 Nc5 22. Nd3 $1 (22. Rb1 O-O $17 {[%cal Ya8c8]}) 22... Nxd3+ 23. Qxd3 Rh7
$1 {[%cal Ge7h4] Black solves his king's problems in a creative way.} 24. Rb3
